In[130]:
def boost(model_adaptive):
    print(' :', model.params['t_grid'])
    print(' :', model_adaptive._t_iterations.sum() - 1)
    print(' ~', model.params['t_grid'] / (model_adaptive._t_iterations.sum() - 1))
